CARIN RTPBC Patient Pay Type Value Set

This value set contains components of a patient's responsibility for a prescription product's cost.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin/CodeSystem/rtpbc-patient-pay-type
